   <sect2 role="installation">
      <title>Installation d'UDFtools</title> 
      
      <para>
         Installez <application>UDFtools</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes: 
      </para> 
      
<screen><userinput>bzcat ../udftools-&udftools-version;.patch.bz2 | patch -Np1 &amp;&amp;
patch -Np1 -i ../udftools-&udftools-version;-fixes-1.patch &amp;&amp;
./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>
      
      <para>
         Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username"> root </systemitem>&nbsp;: 
         
      </para> 
      
<screen role="root">
<userinput>make install</userinput></screen>
      
   </sect2>
   
   <sect2 role="content">
